Id": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1785363159, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 427949238, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "abort \u2014 nothing touched", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "abort \u2014 nothing touched", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "NYeLVc5jDkELd6AGLwrOI", "type": "text", "x": -350, "y": 220, "width": 276.0, "height": 25.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1217745516, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1271484262, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "TECH STACK (all Python)", "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "TECH STACK (all Python)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 20}, {"id": "bVKNzQdtyKStXnSpUcgY4", "type": "text", "x": -350, "y": 270, "width": 672.0, "height": 140.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 620041018, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1053057221, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "docxtpl        pip install docxtpl      Jinja2 inside .docx, keeps ALL styling\njinja2         (dep of docxtpl)          {%p %} paragraph tags, {{ }} values\ndifflib        stdlib                    unified_diff for the approval gate\npython-docx    (dep of docxtpl)          only if you inspect the docx in code\npywin32        Windows only              Word COM -> perfect PDF fidelity\nLibreOffice    external binary           soffice --headless fallback (mac/linux)\n\nno LLM, no GitHub token needed \u2014 sample projects.json drives everything", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "docxtpl        pip install docxtpl      Jinja2 inside .docx, keeps ALL styling\njinja2         (dep of docxtpl)          {%p %} paragraph tags, {{ }} values\ndifflib        stdlib                    unified_diff for the approval gate\npython-docx    (dep of docxtpl)          only if you inspect the docx in code\npywin32        Windows only              Word COM -> perfect PDF fidelity\nLibreOffice    external binary           soffice --headless fallback (mac/linux)\n\nno LLM, no GitHub token needed \u2014 sample projects.json drives everything", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "LhMCmdGhBPCqKAWG97Toh", "type": "text", "x": -350, "y": 560, "width": 626.4, "height": 22.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#f08c00", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1325436104, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1542683077, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "STEP 1 \u2014 MAKE cv_template.docx (one-time, by hand in Word)", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "STEP 1 \u2014 MAKE cv_template.docx (one-time, by hand in Word)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 18}, {"id": "rLSRlro7FOmQMaqbcnrU4", "type": "text", "x": -350, "y": 605, "width": 520.8, "height": 157.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 690876516, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1008261137, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "1. copy your real CV .docx  ->  cv/cv_template.docx\n2. delete the hardcoded Projects entries only\n3. in their place type the docxtpl tags (below)\n4. RULE: type each tag in ONE go, no pausing/editing mid-tag \u2014\n   Word splits interrupted text into runs -> docxtpl\n   'unexpected end of template' error. broken tag? delete\n   the WHOLE tag, retype clean.\n5. keep the bullet line in Word's bullet-list style\n   so {{ b }} renders as real list items", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. copy your real CV .docx  ->  cv/cv_template.docx\n2. delete the hardcoded Projects entries only\n3. in their place type the docxtpl tags (below)\n4. RULE: type each tag in ONE go, no pausing/editing mid-tag \u2014\n   Word splits interrupted text into runs -> docxtpl\n   'unexpected end of template' error. broken tag? delete\n   the WHOLE tag, retype clean.\n5. keep the bullet line in Word's bullet-list style\n   so {{ b }} renders as real list items", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "NxDnvUZehYMVnAqYwO9uI", "type": "text", "x": -350, "y": 830, "width": 310.8, "height": 140.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 789704333, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1836753734, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "{%p for p in projects %}\n{{ p.title }}\nTech: {{ p.tech_stack | join(\", \") }}\n{%p for b in p.bullets %}\n{{ b }}\n{%p endfor %}\n{{ p.repo_url }}\n{%p endfor %}", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "{%p for p in projects %}\n{{ p.title }}\nTech: {{ p.tech_stack | join(\", \") }}\n{%p for b in p.bullets %}\n{{ b }}\n{%p endfor %}\n{{ p.repo_url }}\n{%p endfor %}", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "OJCuHAJYCZat4LREVu2nO", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 560, "width": 302.4, "height": 22.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#f08c00", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1404737381, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1573652188, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "STEP 2 \u2014 fill.py (~20 lines)", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "STEP 2 \u2014 fill.py (~20 lines)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 18}, {"id": "4tBK3QrG9Cn8TGfZbPKXT", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 605, "width": 428.4, "height": 122.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1581610697, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1676093469, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "from docxtpl import DocxTemplate\nimport json\n\ntpl = DocxTemplate(\"cv/cv_template.docx\")\nprojects = json.load(open(\"data/projects.json\"))\ntpl.render({\"projects\": projects}, autoescape=True)\ntpl.save(\"output/cv_filled.docx\")", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "from docxtpl import DocxTemplate\nimport json\n\ntpl = DocxTemplate(\"cv/cv_template.docx\")\nprojects = json.load(open(\"data/projects.json\"))\ntpl.render({\"projects\": projects}, autoescape=True)\ntpl.save(\"output/cv_filled.docx\")", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "HZIkV2rbFHJ7OXdHWffT3", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 760, "width": 411.59999999999997, "height": 105.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 363783342, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 111496652, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "autoescape=True matters: repo READMEs can contain\n& < >  ->  raw they corrupt the docx XML\n\nPASS: open cv_filled.docx next to original \u2014\nfonts, margins, header identical; only\nProjects section differs", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "autoescape=True matters: repo READMEs can contain\n& < >  ->  raw they corrupt the docx XML\n\nPASS: open cv_filled.docx next to original \u2014\nfonts, margins, header identical; only\nProjects section differs", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "NiUOpnVGVyu8PEHSR4zZP", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 960, "width": 324.0, "height": 22.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#f08c00", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 16613952, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1623396833, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "STEP 3 \u2014 review.py (diff gate)", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "STEP 3 \u2014 review.py (diff gate)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 18}, {"id": "Z37NGSXAAjT9xkmAs8dth", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 1005, "width": 613.1999999999999, "height": 105.0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 667933167, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 770658274, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "old = extract_text(previous approved snapshot)\nnew = extract_text(cv_filled.docx)      # python-docx: iterate paragraphs\ndiff = difflib.unified_diff(old, new, \"current CV\", \"proposed CV\")\nprint(diff);  input(\"Apply these changes? [y/N] \")\n'y'  -> convert + save snapshot\nelse -> exit, files untouched (default = safe)", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "old = extract_text(previous approved snapshot)\nnew = extract_text(cv_filled.docx)      # python-docx: iterate paragraphs\ndiff = difflib.unified_diff(old, new, \"current CV\", \"proposed CV\")\nprint(diff);  input(\"Apply these changes? [y/N] \")\n'y'  -> convert + save snapshot\nelse -> exit, files untouched (default = safe)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "4UbDXtmwKLDFB3y46M6I0", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 1160, "width": 452.4, "height": 32.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 2082028861, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1729221157, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "snapshot = plain-text dump of last approved content,\nstored in output/ \u2014 diff is text vs text, not docx vs docx", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "snapshot = plain-text dump of last approved content,\nstored in output/ \u2014 diff is text vs text, not docx vs docx", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 13}, {"id": "4vH7Dnd6XxGFr9OoaDxXS", "type": "text", "x": 1500, "y": 560, "width": 356.4, "height": 22.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#f08c00", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 675557091, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1785730354, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "STEP 4 \u2014 convert.py (docx -> PDF)", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "STEP 4 \u2014 convert.py (docx -> PDF)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 18}, {"id": "jtq1FN9qHjVaY0YfqSgDD", "type": "text", "x": 1500, "y": 605, "width": 537.6, "height": 227.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1303926815, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 81739040, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "try Windows Word COM first (perfect fidelity):\n\n    import win32com.client\n    word = win32com.client.Dispatch(\"Word.Application\")\n    doc = word.Documents.Open(abs_path_docx)\n    doc.SaveAs(abs_path_pdf, FileFormat=17)   # 17 = wdFormatPDF\n    doc.Close(); word.Quit()\n\nfallback LibreOffice (any OS):\n\n    soffice --headless --convert-to pdf\n            --outdir output/ output/cv_filled.docx\n    (subprocess, timeout=60)", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "try Windows Word COM first (perfect fidelity):\n\n    import win32com.client\n    word = win32com.client.Dispatch(\"Word.Application\")\n    doc = word.Documents.Open(abs_path_docx)\n    doc.SaveAs(abs_path_pdf, FileFormat=17)   # 17 = wdFormatPDF\n    doc.Close(); word.Quit()\n\nfallback LibreOffice (any OS):\n\n    soffice --headless --convert-to pdf\n            --outdir output/ output/cv_filled.docx\n    (subprocess, timeout=60)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "Wz4fZmHGjZttesCSwQgyC", "type": "text", "x": 1500, "y": 905, "width": 403.2, "height": 122.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#e03131", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 523528974, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1912595471, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "gotchas:\n- COM needs ABSOLUTE paths, forward slashes fail\n- close any open LibreOffice window first or\n  headless convert silently hangs -> the 60s\n  timeout is what surfaces it\n- LibreOffice substitutes missing fonts ->\n  install the template's fonts or PDF looks off", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "gotchas:\n- COM needs ABSOLUTE paths, forward slashes fail\n- close any open LibreOffice window first or\n  headless convert silently hangs -> the 60s\n  timeout is what surfaces it\n- LibreOffice substitutes missing fonts ->\n  install the template's fonts or PDF looks off", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 14}, {"id": "axSoICa9XmMsxHsuyPpmT", "type": "text", "x": 600, "y": 1320, "width": 990.0, "height": 37.5, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#e03131", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 1414753737, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1330214556, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784470658912, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "BUILD ORDER:  template (riskiest, decides feasibility)  ->  fill.py  ->  convert.py  ->  review.py glue.\nEach step testable alone with the sample projects.json \u2014 commit that sample so this half never needs API keys.", "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "BUILD ORDER:  template (riskiest, decides feasibility)  ->  fill.py  ->  convert.py  ->  review.py glue.\nEach step testable alone with the sample projects.json \u2014 commit that sample so this half never needs API keys.", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 15}], "appState": {"gridSize": null, "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"}, "files": {}}